{"tid":428449,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"[登峯造極]D850締造100分傳奇","createTime":"2017-10-08T05:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T05:57:20.000Z","uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1806153543ccaddae6aafdd15b12d940f6dd7af8","tid":428449,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:27:02.000Z","msg":"D850響DXO Mark上面得到100分，成為第一部獲得100分既相機。但相信日後會有更高分既機出現。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/132649_ca9ac32671f87b747dad1e9cddc44e20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F132649_ca9ac32671f87b747dad1e9cddc44e20.jpg&h=886f60aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/132657_f3e6d9be7dd03e74370e620354e5d901.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F132657_f3e6d9be7dd03e74370e620354e5d901.jpg&h=2536086d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/digital/b434n4n.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fdigital%2Fb434n4n.html&d=4XQIVCbeeCMwHoKAx8ePbdWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=82764341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/digital/b434n4n.html</a><br />\n<br />\n尼康D850的全畫幅背照式傳感器讓它成為第一台拿到100分的DSLR。<br />\nD850的核心競爭力是其低感時極其出色的色深（人像）和動態範圍（風光），它在這兩項上的單項分數基本是我們DXO測試過的相機裡面最好的。最低原生感光度的時候有14.8EV的動態範圍和26.4bit的色深，再加上4570萬的總像素，這台機器無疑在風光、棚拍、人像有著很棒的發揮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/digital/b434n4n.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fdigital%2Fb434n4n.html&d=4XQIVCbeeCMwHoKAx8ePbdWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=82764341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/digital/b434n4n.html</a>"},{"pid":"899b0fb2f2f29918cf14e0fffc464d5f55cb3e14","tid":428449,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:43:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20170904/mobile/bkn-20170904201558487-0904_00982_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20170904%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170904201558487-0904_00982_001.html&d=4XQIVCbeeCMwHoKAx8ePbdWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=a5697946\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20170904/mobile/bkn-20170904201558487-0904_00982_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n以往擁有高像素的單反相機，連拍速度相應會較慢，不過全新Nikon D850單反相機，不僅配備4,575萬像素CMOS和EXPEED 5影像處理器，拍出細膩影像之餘，而且連拍速度更支援每秒9張，感光度甚至可擴展至最高Hi 2（ISO 102,400），適用於商業攝影、Pre-Wedding拍攝、運動攝影等，泛用性相當高，發布會中更邀請了3位人氣攝影師，包括商業/廣告攝影師Emil Tse、縮時攝影創作人Patrick Cheung和婚禮攝影師Jack Chan。 <br />\n<br />\nD850作為D810的後繼機，除了像素高、速度快之外，亦加入了不少新功能，當中包括對焦移動拍攝功能，可設定拍片張數和間隔，Emil指拍攝時相機會自動移動焦距，從而營造長景深的效果，因此現場擺設的模型車，拍攝後再透過軟件後製，出來的效果有如真車一樣。此外，D850亦都支援4K拍片，以及全高清慢動作影片，甚至提供8K縮時短片，Patrick表示擁有4K或8K縮時拍攝，而且支援靜音和曝光平滑化，加上短片可選擇FX或DX格式，令後製各種視角效果更具彈性。至於D850的機背亦新加入上下翻揭式屏幕設計，Jack解釋在婚禮拍攝時，間中需要以高低角度取景，有翻揭式屏幕就毋須瞓身拍攝。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/134252_af787e4e59ee43fdc85ae5d6d4a7cf00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F134252_af787e4e59ee43fdc85ae5d6d4a7cf00.jpg&h=e4dcf15c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/134303_9081a258020cdd50bfd0f2451125de9d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F134303_9081a258020cdd50bfd0f2451125de9d.jpg&h=1126b740&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"caa01233f4efc34951f0a8f771501375d8a21a38","tid":428449,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:50:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/135048_f424ce14b512a47535087ad0f1a94e0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F135048_f424ce14b512a47535087ad0f1a94e0e.jpg&h=78476d4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21965db2e0704890fefe1df7d429c6939bf8dc9c","tid":428449,"uid":27766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:56:04.000Z","msg":"同級嚟講 D700係最後一部"},{"pid":"be04f5ab386ca2eae1aec633127196f18b7f4843","tid":428449,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:57:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同級嚟講 D700係最後一部</blockquote><br />\n？？？"}]}